README for xfce 4.8.x

REQUIREMENTS

PRE-INSTALL

  Be sure that you don't have xfce 4.6.x installed, or remove it.

POST-INSTALL

PRECAUTION

  Update/install ports in the following order:

     - libxfce4util
     - xfconf
     - libxfce4ui (new in 4.8), libxfcegui4 (deprecated since 4.8), garcon (new in 4.8) & exo
     - xfce4-panel
     - thunar
     - xfce4-settings, xfce4-session, xfdesktop, xfwm4, xfce-utils, xfce4-appfinder, ...  
    
  or use prt-get:

    prt-get update `prt-get quickdep xfce4`
